reviewText: Great Dvd with 27 videos........BUT!!!! where is "women in the wall" ???? my favorite song by BS, all in all still a great dvd even if you need to buy a multi region player

I just love the beautiful south and this d v d
has it all .All the classic songs and videos.
Been a fan of The Beautiful South for 20+ years and never had a chance to see many of their videos (doubt they were ever shown in the U.S.), so this was quite a treat to watch.
